From: DevBox UML arm64 Port
Subject: [PATCH] arm64: um: add asm/module.h override to prevent redefinition

arm64 native module.h redefines mod_arch_specific which conflicts with
asm-generic/module.h already included by the UML build.

--- /dev/null
+++ b/arch/arm64/um/asm/module.h
@@ -0,0 +1,8 @@
+/* SPDX-License-Identifier: GPL-2.0 */
+/* UML override: use generic module support, no arm64 PLT/FTRACE extras */
+#ifndef __UM_ARM64_ASM_MODULE_H
+#define __UM_ARM64_ASM_MODULE_H
+
+#include <asm-generic/module.h>
+
+#endif
